            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "id": 6030962,
            "title": "〈台股開盤〉震盪翻黑跌逾百點失守2萬2及半年線 安控、塑化、伺服器竄出頭",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美股 19 日休市，台股今 (20) 日早盤以平低盤 21960.51 點開出，下跌 42.99 點，台積電等權值股多無明顯表態，儘管在塑化、AI 類股走強下，指數一度由黑翻紅，最高漲近百點，但遭逢 5 日線壓力漲幅收斂，由紅翻黑跌逾百點，跌破 22000 點及半年線，早盤預估估全日成交量 3304 億元。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6030962/l/7f384dd36ecabb2c75748295b86b716b.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台股開盤〉權值股無力陷入震盪 安控、塑化、伺服器竄出頭。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>權值股表現平淡，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSM-US</a>) 持平，維持 1035 元；聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 下跌 5 元，跌約 0.5%；廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 漲約 1%，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>)、日月光投控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>) (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>) 均持平，聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>) 遊走於平盤下方。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>緯創 AI 伺服器訂單需求強勁，竹北工廠日 (19) 前開幕，激勵伺服器類股走強，機殼類股，勤誠 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8210:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8210\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8210-TW</a>) 漲約 4%，晟銘電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3013:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3013\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3013-TW</a>) 漲約 1%；緯創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3231:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3231\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3231-TW</a>) 漲逾 2%，緯穎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6669:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6669\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6669-TW</a>) 漲約 1%，和碩 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4938:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4938\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4938-TW</a>) 走強。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>以伊衝突惡化，油價持續上漲，油氣燃電股受激勵，台塑化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6505:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6505\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6505-TW</a>) 漲約 1%；塑化類股同樣走強，華夏 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1305:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1305\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1305-TW</a>) 漲逾 1%，台達化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1309:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1309\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1309-TW</a>) 漲約 1%，聯成 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1313:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1313\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1313-TW</a>)、台聚 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1304:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1304\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1304-TW</a>) 均走揚。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>安控國家隊題材持續發酵，安控股走強，杭特 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3297:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3297\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3297-TW</a>) 亮紅燈，天鉞電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5251:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5251\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5251-TW</a>) 漲約 6%，昇銳 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3128:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3128\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3128-TW</a>) 漲逾 5%，慧友 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5484:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5484\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5484-TW</a>) 漲約 2%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
